        "editorNotes": "Altaria is the only Dragon to see widespread play in the current meta, and Goodra presents few advantages over it. Its middling stats and non-STAB attacks give it a soft matchup profile that allows it to play as a corebreaker, but it it lacks the strength as a generalist to truly succeed."
